{"tid":1882223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「最新消息」新鴻基同信和果班商場業主 睇完租戶條數 話依幾個月跌幅好小 唔關示威同肺炎事 唔批準商戶減租申請","createTime":"2020-02-16T06:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T03:16:54.000Z","uid":252492,"like":226,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb03682c984e943f3cf0dbad728c9c6d30d9d28","tid":1882223,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"特別係新鴻基 賣撚哂新聞話有經營困難商戶2月可以減租<br />\n點知成堆商戶交哂條數比佢申請 話依幾個月都係咁上下無咩跌幅唔批減租申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8dfdfa5cc4feded1eab167875f254a6f6421ec9","tid":1882223,"uid":252492,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:17:24.000Z","msg":"小租戶批新地：佢哋喺地球上消失咗<br />\n不過，業主與商戶共渡時艱，卻非必然的事。陳與其代表食肆，於過去數月不斷與新地及九倉就減租不停交涉，「佢嘅租務部都會叫我去寫信，但係通常得返嚟嘅回覆都係話冇，尤其是新鴻基，話一毫子都唔會減，而家直頭喺地球上消失咗。」至於九倉，上月有報道指有商戶經磋商多時，終獲減租約半年，減幅約15%至20%，「我就冇受惠嘅，但我知嘅係如果租約就完，呢幾個月減租就會易傾啲。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20200108/60460858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200108%2F60460858&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=19f9a067\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200108%2F60460858&h=0767717d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20200108/60460858</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lhe9fBn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLhe9fBn.png&h=1db55097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u7Exdn8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu7Exdn8.png&h=ca414f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/61fTHgx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F61fTHgx.png&h=640ac13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n信和：依幾個月有出通告話商場唔開既日子先賠租 中間2 3點有示威或防暴商場落閘逼商戶關門趕顧客走既日子全部唔賠<br />\n<br />\n新地：近排已經攪左好多會員推廣吸引人流 唔會減租或免租 之前落閘既日子都唔會賠<br />\n<br />\n10月同11月好多大商場都有好多非大連鎖店既細鋪已經執鳩哂<br />\n可以留意下大商場d冷行已經變哂吉鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大地產商回應商場租戶 話近日社會已經回復平靜 已經無哂周圍破壞同蹤火 商場集會阻礙營業 唔會減租或免租共渡時艱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778223\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"50c5dd5056de6c979d51e13c3457a16e2380efd7","tid":1882223,"uid":252492,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"3cb03682c984e943f3cf0dbad728c9c6d30d9d28","tid":1882223,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"特別係新鴻基 賣撚哂新聞話有經營困難商戶2月可以減租<br />\n點知成堆商戶交哂條數比佢申請 話依幾個月都係咁上下無咩跌幅唔批減租申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tpD9D20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtpD9D20.png&h=130d19f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新鴻基：睇完盤數 無咩點跌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7c043e24cfaa27499583a46bfddd03eba50072","tid":1882223,"uid":93318,"like":92,"dislike":6,"score":86,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:28:43.000Z","msg":"支持SHK<br />\n經營不善關人鬼事"},{"pid":"27821c90313b0229d0737374dbdbd34f439480a9","tid":1882223,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"系你老母<br />\n汁你老豆<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"1f864300bdde76ddc256f8106cc42cf90bf124a2","tid":1882223,"uid":252492,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"27821c90313b0229d0737374dbdbd34f439480a9","tid":1882223,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"系你老母<br />\n汁你老豆<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"facebook留言關我閪事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1493f9c41b6f69e